  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mitigating the spread of Ebola through community sensitisation and health and hygiene awareness</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of the program is to raise awareness of the Ebola virus and its modes of transmission, and to reduce the rate of infection and related morbidity and mortality among the general population. The response is focused on prevention with most activities designed to support the Communication Pillar: 
